Distribution. Norway ( Thor 1931a ), Poland ( Michocka 1987 ), Hungary (
Ripka et al . 2005
). Remarks. Michocka (1987: 31) apparently figured trichobothria on tibiae II, a characteristic only found in the subfamily Odontoscirinae; it is likely that the species reported from Poland might be the result of a misidentification.
